     * [../Debian-and-Windows-Shared-Printing/index.html]
       Debian-and-Windows-Shared-Printing, Debian and Windows Shared
       Printing mini-HOWTO
       Updated: Jul 2005. Demonstrates how to use command-line tools to
       configure your Debian system for printing. It explains how to
       send documents from Linux to Windows printers and how to share
       Linux printers with Windows PCs.
     * [../Print2Win.html] Print2Win, The Linux Print2Win mini-HOWTO
       Updated: Jul 2002. Contains the general configuration to get
