     * [../Secure-Programs-HOWTO/index.html] Secure-Programs-HOWTO,
       Secure Programming for Linux and Unix HOWTO
       Updated: Mar 2003. Provides a set of design and implementation
       guidelines for writing secure programs for Linux and Unix
       systems.
