     * [../Belarusian-HOWTO/index.html] Belarusian-HOWTO, Linux
       Belarusian mini-HOWTO
       Updated: Feb 2001. Short guide in setting up Belarusian language
       support in Linux console, X Window System, web-browsers, text
       editors, etc. Charsets described are windows-1251, iso-8859-5 and
       koi8-ru. Written in English.
